# Normalize all text source to LF. Windows dev + Linux Docker containers
# don't mix well otherwise - hit this exact problem twice: entrypoint.sh's
# shebang broke with CRLF, and mixed-endings crept into other source files
# after a git reset --hard checked them out with core.autocrlf converting
# them on the way in.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Shell scripts and Dockerfiles specifically must never be CRLF, regardless
# of a user's local core.autocrlf setting - CRLF breaks the shebang when
# these run inside Linux containers.
*.sh text eol=lf
Dockerfile text eol=lf
